p.e:
OCTOBER 31ST

SOMETHING'S NOT RIGHT.
THE TOWNSFOLK HAVE BEEN
AVOIDING MY GAZE ALL DAY
TODAY.

I OVER-HEARD CHATTER ABOUT
ALL HALLOW'S EVE TONIGHT.

I SHALL VENTURE OUT TO
INVESTIGATE SOME OF MY
EARLIER SUSPICIONS BREWING
THROUGHOUT THE PAST MONTH
I HAVE LIVED ON RAVENSWICH
ISLE...


--AARON WINCHESTERSON
